rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會<br />\n炸雞賣唔曬會倒"},{"pid":"c4bac55b444979c79112d540bcae88af426d77db","tid":8353,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"葡撻係廚房整定急凍？"},{"pid":"24cfb78f1a37526627800c8820d1354b4b3e53eb","tid":8353,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢人工 啲雞擺左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我做果陣仲係31蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最高峰都試過33架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90356e560ca59c5e5f852ec56683e246a23ffab","tid":8353,"uid":30323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪好多老鼠， o 的油係咪成呎厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n久唔久有一、兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲油隔幾日就會清一清<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做過一排"},{"pid":"8cbca9e28f163d874f4d97b3a43c265e3544d47d","tid":8353,"uid":23919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"大盛餐好抵食 下個月仲有冇？"},{"pid":"553b934a97b454dd5714429b6c63ea0ee5291c9f","tid":8353,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"KFC依家扮吉野家是否on9"},{"pid":"89145c3372bb7b1cc96971c8cee06bd4553ef3e0","tid":8353,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪好多老鼠， o 的油係咪成呎厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老鼠好少見 曱甴就有<br />\n油就一定多 我食果陣d油都飛撚曬出黎"},{"pid":"ad58defa429de0b0b9761639de4978e2a7e35108","tid":8353,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大盛餐好抵食 下個月仲有冇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇做兩年啦