l/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇"},{"pid":"a96949d87ad7dd9ab43ed369c384413fabe4cd7b","tid":8353,"uid":22370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"香蜜鬆餅點解愈黎愈低質？"},{"pid":"24633c451b011753afc77a52a23507b617baef11","tid":8353,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39c156d81d7f9bf7556e66b2c291a03d6388f7d2","tid":8353,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>D飯係咪會隔夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNo</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能你之前做個間唔會，我上次食到隔夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c056ecd7c9542d8bc42d4e9b4f4de64e1d9c83","tid":8353,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"慈雲山間kfc真係狗也不屌"},{"pid":"05fc33c8acb67dd664c22de23d786296c963868e","tid":8353,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"係咪好污糟？自己會唔會食？"},{"pid":"286c85331a64ad79b179b5417a62047ba72ec982","tid":8353,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>員工的關係淫不？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淫就唔算淫 不過會互溝囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你知啦 做得kfc都係青春活潑既學生妹 唔係唔撩下呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果d正少少既女就緊係要收下兵啦 家常便飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5037b308e247b3a82b09be51ff47