幾好 所有野都唔隔夜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為大筒飯因爲平，所以畀隔夜飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa8ee0b62c56fa7918e29a5c88d964a857c8255","tid":8353,"uid":22370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香蜜鬆餅點解愈黎愈低質？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前兩年食仲好撚好食喎 放工都要夾幾舊返屋企食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學嗰時真係好撚好食，而家已經差咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要買親都俾人話啲呀婆呀伯先會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76e875f110a45fb73adf4b5527ddb867eb8618f","tid":8353,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪好污糟？自己會唔會食？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我地呢間都幾好 舊雞跌左落張枱經理已經會叫我地掉 <br />\n不過其實去邊食都污糟架啦 所以我自己返工都會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e5168d478c5ae02eb4216371f5d718285d200a","tid":8353,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個芝士醬係現成定溝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溝既係點溝嫁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以我睇係現成"},{"pid":"4f88afe39bccad4c865429bd35aaa946cd76faba","tid":8353,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"巴打做緊STAR定主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜屈係KFC發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27cc78f17ea8a504373c595d4e3c6ae97276093","tid":8353,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香蜜鬆餅點解愈黎愈低質？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前兩年食仲好撚好食喎 放工都要夾幾舊返屋企食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><